<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9999.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9999.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9999.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9999.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9999"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_0001.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_0001.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_0001.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_0001.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_0001"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_0002.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_0002.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_0002.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_0002.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_0002"/></a></p>

<p>その後、ワールドポーターズをぶらぶらする。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_0008.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_0008.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_0008.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_0008.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_0008"/></a></p>
