<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9987.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9987.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9987.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9987.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9987"/></a>
