<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9845.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9845.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9845.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9845.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9845"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9847.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9847.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9847.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9847.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9847"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9848.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9848.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9848.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9848.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9848"/></a>
<a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9849.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9849.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9849.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9849.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9849"/></a></p>

<p>外飲みなので暑い。涼しさを求めて2軒目へ。</p>

<p>おちょこ2つ出てきたけど娘には飲ませてませんよ。</p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://tabelog.com/tokyo/A1301/A130103/13032695/">魚金 4号店</a>
