  <item rdf:about="2024/0717-odaiba/">
            <title>2024/07/17: お台場</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2024/0717-odaiba/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>会社イベントでお台場へ。<a href="https://hado-official.com/">HADO</a>なるARスポーツ。</p>

<p><a href="https://www.don.to/diary/600/img_9822.jpg" class="image swipe"><img src="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9822.jpg" srcset="https://www.don.to/diary/96/img_9822.jpg 1x, https://www.don.to/diary/192/img_9822.jpg 2x" height="96" alt="img_9822"/></a>
